WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.640 --> 00:00:02.400
All right, we have enough to start.

00:00:02.575 --> 00:00:07.920
When you come in, tell us where you're from and how your weather is today.

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:11.200
I hear the sound of an abundance of rain.

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.520
How about you?

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:16.104
I'm calling forth the rain over Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:00:16.104 --> 00:00:22.200
Oklahoma needs rain now, and we're going to bring it in in Jesus' name.

00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:25.715
Thank you for joining us.

00:00:26.145 --> 00:00:30.160
We'll just jump right into the river here; I have an urgency in my spirit.

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:37.680
The Lord said, "I want you on," and we did our best here, but we've got a lot of work to do.

00:00:38.503 --> 00:00:43.920
We're going to pray over certain things the Lord has brought up to my spirit today.

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:46.600
He said, "I want you to pray over Minnesota.

00:00:48.080 --> 00:00:49.929
I want you to pray over Mike Lindell.

00:00:49.929 --> 00:00:51.727
He needs some covering right now.

00:00:51.727 --> 00:00:55.440
There's some things that he's going through that nobody knows, obviously.

00:00:55.440 --> 00:01:01.920
" And the Lord said, "You bring it to the people tonight and pray over Mike Lindell, the pillow man.

00:01:02.255 --> 00:01:05.844
" He's going to win; I believe with all my heart he's going to win.

00:01:05.844 --> 00:01:15.910
But he needs some covering in the spirit; undergirding is what I want to call it—a little push.

00:01:15.910 --> 00:01:18.240
So we're going to pray for Mike Lindell tonight.

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:20.265
That was on my heart all day.

00:01:20.265 --> 00:01:23.387
And then the other thing was praying over Passover.

00:01:23.387 --> 00:01:24.693
It has started now.

00:01:24.693 --> 00:01:30.120
It's already tomorrow in Australia, I believe.

00:01:30.525 --> 00:01:44.286
We're going to pray over Passover, specifically over the United States and the synagogues where the Jewish people gather, for protection in and around the areas where they might be doing their services.

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:47.093
But the Lord put this on my heart.

00:01:47.093 --> 00:01:56.568
He said, "Pray for them against terrorist attacks, against mass Mass shootings events, and so on.

00:01:57.784 --> 00:02:07.760
" The Lord warned us a lot about the first, which is just a couple of hours from now here in the central part of America.

00:02:08.089 --> 00:02:17.110
He said that it would be a doubling—that we would now see the doubling of where we were from Passover on, going into the next six months.

00:02:17.110 --> 00:02:19.657
We're going to see an acceleration of things.

00:02:19.657 --> 00:02:23.125
And he said this is a time that we need to pray even more.

00:02:23.420 --> 00:02:29.053
I'm so thankful for every one of you who came out so quickly to pray with us.

00:02:29.933 --> 00:02:35.560
I'm not used to just jumping right into the river here, but I've been instructed.

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:38.131
So let's take communion real quick.

00:02:38.131 --> 00:02:42.920
I know this is getting really fast, but let's take communion.

00:02:42.920 --> 00:02:45.600
Father, I just thank you for your body.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:47.973
I thank you, Father, that you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:02:47.973 --> 00:02:50.480
You were bruised for our iniquities.

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:54.960
The chastisement of our peace was upon you and with your stripes we are healed.

00:02:54.960 --> 00:03:04.880
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that just like we always are believing that today is the expiration date of whatever they're believing for tonight.

00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:13.051
I thank you, Father, that as we pray as believing believers, we're not beggars.

00:03:13.051 --> 00:03:17.400
We're not going before the Father begging.

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:18.420
We're not beggars.

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:22.840
We're believers, and we receive what he said we could have.

00:03:22.840 --> 00:03:27.537
And I believe tonight there's many of you that will get your breakthrough as we're in prayer tonight.

00:03:27.537 --> 00:03:34.345
You'll get your breakthrough in your body as we're interceding for the nations, as we're interceding for the things the Lord has called us to pray for.

00:03:34.345 --> 00:03:36.480
Believe for your miracle.

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:46.218
It's time for the body of Christ to be that body and to arise and shine for the light has come and the glory of the Lord has risen on us.

00:03:46.218 --> 00:03:48.800
It's time for us to be salty.

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.760
We must be salty.

00:03:50.760 --> 00:03:53.280
We cannot lose our saltiness.

00:03:53.280 --> 00:04:03.507
We have to be that light in the darkness that whenever the people see it in the days ahead, no matter how dark the world gets, the church gets lighter and lighter.

00:04:05.400 --> 00:04:08.638
That we are that church, that glorious body.

00:04:11.160 --> 00:04:12.903
We are the glorious church.

00:04:12.903 --> 00:04:15.640
The glorious body is rising up in these last days.

00:04:15.640 --> 00:04:27.130
And it's time that we take our dominion and our authority and be that backbone like a crowbar and tell the devil he's not taking our stuff.

00:04:27.130 --> 00:04:37.907
If we don't stand up and do this and do what we're supposed to do for Canada, praying over Canada when I told you what I saw concerning Canada, the devil's just going to run you right over.

00:04:37.907 --> 00:04:45.033
You have to put that with the authority of the believer, like a police officer.

00:04:45.033 --> 00:04:48.126
It's the authority of the government that backs him.

00:04:48.126 --> 00:04:51.406
It's the power of the government that backs the police officer.

00:04:51.406 --> 00:04:53.707
A police officer by himself doesn't have anything.

00:04:53.707 --> 00:04:55.720
He just stands up there with a stop sign.

00:04:55.720 --> 00:05:04.320
But it's because of who backs him: the law, the law of the land, the United States government.

00:05:14.831 --> 00:05:15.107
When he says 'Stop,' you stop immediately because you know there's consequences if you don't.

00:05:20.800 --> 00:05:25.720
And as a believing believer who knows who they are, as He is, so are we in this world.

00:05:30.300 --> 00:05:30.640
When we put up our Holy Ghost stop sign, that devil better stop.

00:05:42.394 --> 00:05:42.709
And so we know that whenever a Christian is is ignorant and doesn't know who they are in Christ, the devil knows.

00:05:42.709 --> 00:05:45.084
When you know, the devil knows when you know.

00:05:45.084 --> 00:05:51.470
He knows immediately by the way you act, by being a begging believer versus being a believing believer.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:05:58.970
And you're the one that says, 'Hey, I know who I am, whom I serve, who's living on the inside of me.

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:07.360
And I know that I have authority over you because Jesus Christ gave it to me.

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:09.175
' And I thank you.

00:06:13.771 --> 00:06:14.046
It's all right.

00:06:14.046 --> 00:06:15.595
I have a nickel, son.

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:32.166
But that's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:06:32.166 --> 00:06:38.120
As far as a quarter goes, I told you it'd be that thin.

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:42.480
You're going to see the darkness of this world get darker and darker with labor pains.

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:45.577
As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:06:55.680 --> 00:06:55.905
And then you're going to see the glorious church rise.

00:07:01.200 --> 00:07:01.697
But it's your choice what side you want to look at every day.

00:07:04.183 --> 00:07:05.423
You can look at all the drama.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:16.107
You can look at what's going on with Facebook and all this other, or you can look at what the Bible says.

00:07:17.151 --> 00:07:18.747
We're the victorious church, the blood-bought, the church, the redeemed.

00:07:18.747 --> 00:07:20.160
But it's your choice.

00:07:20.160 --> 00:07:22.860
You have to choose every single day.

00:07:26.465 --> 00:07:27.170
I will focus on what God has called me to do.

00:07:30.700 --> 00:07:34.640
And I will not allow my mind to wander and go, "Oh, what about the sky's falling, Chicken Little?

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:45.680
" And that's why I'm not saying it's not falling.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:53.080
I believe with all my heart the best days are yet to come for the church, for us, the remnant.

00:07:53.080 --> 00:07:54.880
But yes, we're going to see some things.

00:07:55.213 --> 00:08:02.154
And I've warned you time and time again about the things the Lord has showed me.

00:08:02.154 --> 00:08:04.420
But does it have to affect you?

00:08:04.420 --> 00:08:07.960
Am I going to participate in economic struggles?

00:08:07.960 --> 00:08:10.220
Are you going to participate in economic struggles?

00:08:10.220 --> 00:08:17.475
I don't know about you in your house, but as for me and my house, we're going to serve the Lord.

00:08:31.405 --> 00:08:31.620
And I believe that the Bible says I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:08:33.620 --> 00:08:38.687
And that whenever I give, it shall be given unto me: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over shall men give unto our bosom.

00:08:38.687 --> 00:08:42.942
I believe that the wealth of the sinners is laid up for the righteous.

00:08:42.942 --> 00:08:51.229
But you have to be a believing believer that is fully persuaded that what God has promised, he's able also to perform it.

00:08:51.229 --> 00:08:59.547
And if you're not fully persuaded, the devil's going to know and he's going to be knocking on your door.

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:10.840
So, we're going to stand tonight.

00:09:13.010 --> 00:09:13.375
We're going to take our communion.

00:09:16.935 --> 00:09:27.224
And we're believing believers that are fully persuaded that what Jesus Christ did on that cross—he suffered and he died for every single one of us.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:44.590
That we don't have to have sickness in our body.

00:09:49.314 --> 00:09:49.646
We don't have to have disease.

00:09:49.646 --> 00:09:53.227
He took it all for us.

00:09:53.956 --> 00:09:58.777
And at the finished work of Jesus Christ, at the finished work of the cross, he said, "It is finished.

00:09:58.777 --> 00:10:07.051
" Everything he set out to do for us to have victory over sickness, disease, poverty, lack, over the devil in every area of our life.

00:10:07.926 --> 00:10:12.813
We have authority and he gave it to us whenever he said, "It is finished.

00:10:14.029 --> 00:10:16.034
" And he rose again on that third day.

00:10:16.034 --> 00:10:17.772
That's what resurrection week's all about.

00:10:17.772 --> 00:10:24.209
So, thank you, Father, for what you did for us.

00:10:26.560 --> 00:10:30.800
And we take this in the name of Jesus in remembrance of what you did.

00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:36.050
Now, Lord, we say we make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

00:10:44.811 --> 00:10:45.160
Father, we thank you, Lord.

00:10:45.160 --> 00:10:52.340
We plead the blood of Jesus all around my house, all around my children, all around my wife.

00:10:54.503 --> 00:10:56.463
Father, I thank you, Lord, that the blood covers our finances, covers us.

00:10:58.800 --> 00:11:00.240
Father, I thank you, Lord, that it never loses its power.

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:02.600
We're so grateful for the blood of Jesus.

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:08.560
We're so grateful that we are the blood-bought, the church, the redeemed.

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:17.440
And I plead the blood and I apply the blood over this live stream tonight, over the internet connection, over all the people watching tonight.

00:11:17.440 --> 00:11:24.120
Father, we thank you, Lord, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:28.684
We say, 'Satan, you're under our feet and you will not disrupt in any way.

00:11:28.969 --> 00:11:34.107
I call clarity of thought over my mind and that I think like I'm supposed to of clarity of thought.

00:11:34.107 --> 00:11:37.120
' And Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:45.620
We take authority over any hexes, vexes, or anybody trying to curse us while we're doing it.

00:12:02.100 --> 00:12:02.240
And we bless those that try to come against us.

00:12:05.406 --> 00:12:05.697
And we forgive them, Father.

00:12:06.765 --> 00:12:11.463
And we thank you, Lord, that they're going to get born again.

00:12:16.100 --> 00:12:16.530
For love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:12:26.760 --> 00:12:27.063
And we thank you, Lord, that tonight we forgive our enemies.

00:12:29.930 --> 00:12:30.105
We forgive those that persecute us.

00:12:30.105 --> 00:12:39.250
But every tongue that rises against us, we condemn those words and they fall to the ground.

00:12:39.250 --> 00:12:44.833
Father, we thank you, Lord, for the blood right now in Jesus' name.

00:12:44.833 --> 00:12:46.253
All right.

00:12:46.253 --> 00:12:53.547
Now, I thank you, Lord, that I hear your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:12:53.547 --> 00:13:02.520
If you want to say anything to me, Father, through visions or anything in the spirit, Father, I thank you.

00:13:02.520 --> 00:13:04.270
