00:13:53.360 --> 00:13:53.600
You could use anybody.

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:56.880
But I thank you, Father, that you use me once again.

00:13:58.053 --> 00:14:09.712
And I yield myself over to you, Holy Spirit, that you pray through me, that we pray together, and we get the job done in Jesus' name.

00:14:09.712 --> 00:14:11.440
All right.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:17.916
